" Auto-off IME {{{
if executable('ibus')
  " IM OFF command
  command! ImeOff silent !ibus engine 'xkb:us::eng'

  " When in insert mode
  augroup InsertHook
      autocmd!
      autocmd InsertLeave * ImeOff
  augroup END
elseif executable('fcitx-remote')
  " IM OFF command
  command! ImeOff silent !fcitx-remote -c

  " When in insert mode
  augroup InsertHook
      autocmd!
      autocmd InsertLeave * ImeOff
  augroup END
endif
" }}}
